exploitedteensasia.com puts out some interesting porn, but this video lives up to the web site?s odd name. The woman looks like an exploited teen prostitute, completely uninterested, letting some guy fuck her to get money to pay the rent. Even though there is a camera on her she doesn't pretend to like it, and in fact looks completely bored. Forget being bad porn, this is bad sex. It gives Thai women a bad name. 

(The guy doesn't wear a condom, even when doing anal. There is a lot of AIDS in Thailand, so if she is really a hooker off the street that is just weird.)
